food.name: Pizza
food.description: Pizza is a savory dish of Italian origin, consisting of a usually round, flattened base of leavened wheat-based dough topped with tomatoes, cheese, and often meat, often with added vegetables or sauce.

food.name: Garlic Bread
food.description: Garlic bread is a type of bread made with garlic and other spices. It is a staple food in many cultures, including the United States and the United Kingdom.

food.name: pasta
food.description: Pasta is a type of food typically made from an unleavened dough of durum wheat flour, traditionally mixed with water or eggs, and formed into sheets or other shapes, then cooked by baking or boiling.

food.name: Spaghetti
food.description: Spaghetti is a type of pasta, typically a flat, dry, thin, round, or roundish, made from an unleavened dough of durum wheat flour, traditionally mixed with water or eggs, and formed into sheets or other shapes, then cooked by baking or boiling.

food.name: Burger
food.description: A hamburger is a sandwich consisting of one or more cooked patties of ground meat, usually beef, placed inside a sliced bread roll or bun.

food.name: pancakes
food.description: Pancakes are a type of food typically made with a flat, round, pancake-like dough, which is then fried at a high temperature, traditionally in a hot buttermilk sauce.

food.name: french fries
food.description: French fries are deep-fried, very thin, salted slices of potato that are usually served at room temperature

food.name: hotdog
food.description: A hotdog is a food consisting of a grilled or steamed sausage served in the slit of a partially sliced bun

food.name: Biryani
food.description: Biryani is a type of Indian food made with rice, meat, and vegetables. It is a staple food in many cultures, including the Indian subcontinent, the Himalayas, and the Indian Ocean.

food.name: Butter chicken
food.description: Butter chicken is a type of chicken dish, which is made by frying a piece of chicken in butter and then frying it in a sauce.

food.name: Chicken tikka
food.description: Chicken tikka is a type of chicken dish, which is made by frying a piece of chicken in butter and then frying it in a sauce.

food.name: Samosa
food.description: A samosa is a fried or baked pastry with a savory filling, including ingredients such as spiced potatoes, onions, and peas. It may take different forms, including triangular, cone, or half-moon shapes, depending on the region.

food.name: Prawns
food.description: Prawns are a type of fish that are found in the ocean and are a popular food in the Asian subcontinent.

food.name: Kaeng
food.description: Kaeng is a dish in Thai cuisine made from curry paste, coconut milk or water, meat, seafood, vegetables or fruit, and herbs.

food.name: Thai noodles
food.description: Thai noodles are a type of noodle that is made from rice, usually with a variety of vegetables and meat.

food.name: Tom yum goong
food.description: Tom yum goong is a type of Thai food made from rice, meat, and vegetables. It is a staple food in many cultures, including the Indian subcontinent, the Himalayas, and the Indian Ocean.
